 Liau7 kun Sam-tiong7, ju7-mia5 To7-siu, si7 Ka-gi7 thiaN Sai-le5 kau3-hoe7 Liau7 Seng5-phi TiuN2-lo2 e5 te7-saN sio2-ti7.
 Kun chu7-se3 bo5 pe7, siu7 koaN2-bo2 kap toa7-hiaN eng7 Ki-tok-kau3 ke-teng5 e5 kau3-iok8. Chap8-ji7-hoe3 chiu7 jip8 Sin-lau5 Tiong-oh8, lek8-ni5 kho2-chhi3 long2 liat8 iu-teng2. Chai7 oh8-tiong siu7 se2-le2. Kun thian-chu beng5-bin2, gi7-lun7 chhiong3-heng5, hou7 tong-si5 e5 sian-siN kap peng5-iu2 sou2 khi3-tiong7; put-chai5 kap kun tong5-chhong nng7-ni5 ku2, siu7-tioh8 bo5 khi3-hiam5 khoaN3 cho3 ti-ki2; m7-na7 thiaN3-sioh kun e5 chai5-cheng5, ia7 it-hoat keng3-hok8 kun e5 cho3-lang5. Kun 15 hoe3 sit-loh8 te7-it thiaN3 e5 koaN2-bo2. Chap8-lak8-hoe3 chut-giap8 Tiong-oh8. Hit-tiap8 sim u7 sou2 kam2-tong7, khoaN3-phoa3 se3-cheng5, koat-i3 jip8 Sin-lau5 Hok-im-chu-iN7 kang2-kiu3 sin5-hak8 beh pi7-pan7 cho3 thoan5-kau3 e5 kang. Si7 chai ai3 chin2-kiu3 tong5-pau, chin2-heng bun5-hoa3, bo5 m7-si7 beh kou2-bu2 Ki-tok-kau3 e5 cheng-sin5; kun e5 sim-chi3 tui3 an2-ne hian2-beng5. 
 Kun chai7 Sin5-hak8 tiong ka-ti7 chai iau2-boe7 u7 kau3-giah8, chin ti3-i3 ai3 koh liu5-hak8 Loe7-te7; bat kui2-na7 pai2 tui3 goa2 kong2-chhut chit ho7 chi3-khi3. Kho2-sioh sui-jian5 hak8-chu jiau5-ji7, na7-si7 si3-piN e5 keng2-gu7 m7 in2, si5 boe7 kau3 chi3 boe7 chiaN5. M7-chai si7 in-ui7 khin5-thak8 siuN koe3-thau5, a2-si7 in-ui7 sit-i3 bo5 chhun-chhoa2; chai7 sin5-hak8 e5 te7-saN ni5 ti3 nau2-peN7, koe3 PheN5-ou5 ia7 koh tng2-khi3 chhu3--nih8 tiau7-iong2. Koe3-ni5 peN7 khah ho2 chiah koh lai5 Tai5-lam5 chiap-soa3 thak8-chheh. Chut-giap8 au7, kun bo5 sit-loh8 eng2-jit8 e5 chi3-khi3, tit-tioh8 toa7-hiaN kap Kau3-su7-hoe7 e5 in2-chun2 lai5 Tang-kiaN thak8 Beng5-ti7-hak8-iN7. Kun si7 Tai5-oan5 sin5-hak8 e5 hak8-seng thau5 chit8 e5 lai5 liu5-hak8-e5. 
 Beng5-ti7 41 ni5 2 goeh8 11 ho7 Ki2-goan5-cheh, chiu7-si7 kun Sin5-hou7(Kobe) chiuN7-hoaN7 e5 ki3-liam7-jit8. Hit si5 kun 23 hoe3. Kun kau3 Tang-kiaN liau2-au7 koe3 nng7 le2-pai3 goa2 ia7 lai5 KiaN-tou chiap-tioh8 kun e5 phoe kong2, “Goa2 e5 sim-goan7 sui-jian5 chiok, na7-si7 goa2 e5 siang7 ho2 e5 si5-chun7 i2-keng teh-beh koe3.” 嗚呼! Kun e5 khou2-sim thang chai. Beng5-ti7 43 ni5 3 goeh8 chiu7 chut-giap8 Beng5-ti7-hak8-iN7 e5 Phou2-thong-pou7. Hoan-tng2 ni5 4 goeh8 jip8 Cho2-tiu7-tian5(Waseda) Tai7-hak8 bun5-kho. Kun chai7 Tang-kiaN 4 ni5 ku2 bo5 be7-ki3-tit in2-chhoa7 hia e5 tong5-pan lai5 chiu7-kin7 to7-li2, chiu7 kap Tan5 Bok8-su saN-kap siat-chiaN5 Ko-sa Ki-tok-kau3 Chheng-lian5-hoe7. Tak8 le2-pai3 hoe7-oan5 chu7-chip8 ti7 Hu3-su7-kian3-teng e5 kau3-hoe7.
 Goa2 43 ni5 chhun-thiN lai5 Tang-kiaN tham3-mng7 kun, u7 chhin-bak8 khoaN3-kiN3 chit-e5 hoe7 e5 oah8-tang7. Kau3 taN hoe7 e5 heng5-sek sui-jian5 ke2-oaN7, na7-si7 cheng-sin5 iau2 ti7-teh; kun sou2 cho3 e5 kang be7 bo5-khi3. Si7 kun peng5-seng khoaN3 sin3 Chu2 cho3 cheng3 ti3-sek e5 goan5-thau5, chit8 to7 e5 leng5-hoe2 put-si5 ti7 sim lai7 teh toh8. KHo2-sioh e7 e5 lang5 kau7 tioh8-boa5; 45 ni5 chhun-thiN ku7-peN7 koh hoat-choh, kou-put-chiong tioh8 hiu-hak8 tng2-lai5 Tai5-oan5 tiau5-iong2. Liau2-au7 peN7-cheng5 hoan2-khi2 hoan2-to2, koh lai5 Kiu2-chiu Hok-kong(Fukuoka) chhi3 jip8 Tai7-hak8 peN7-iN7 taN2-tiap8. Put-heng7 chiah8 ioh8 bo5 eng3-hau7. Tai7-cheng3 3 ni5 8 goeh8 12 ho7 kou-sin koe3-ong2 ti7 cho3 lang5-kheh e5 sou2-chai7, hiong2-siu7 29 hoe3. 嗚呼! Ai--chai3! Kun e5 si2 un2-tang3 m7-tan7-na7 kun e5 hiaN-ti7, ke-koan3, chhin-chhek teh siong-pi. SaN-chap8-hoe3 ho7-cho3 chong3, pang3-sak poaN3-si3 e5 seng-gai5 khin5-khou2 eng7 kang, poe7 chheh-siuN tang phun sai chau2, ia7 ng3-bang7 beh thang chiong sou2 tit--tioh8 moa2-pak e5 keng-lun5 lai5 hian3 cho3 Siong7-chu2 chin2-heng pun2-to2 bun5-hoa3 e5 lou7-eng7; na7-si7 beh thai3 u7 phah-sng3 “Chhut-su bi7 chiat8 sin sian song3, tiong5 su2 eng-hiong5 le7 tiam2 khim.” (Chhut-cheng boe7 iaN5 seng-khu tai7-seng si2, ku2-ku2 hou7 eng-hiong5 e5 bak8-sai2 lau5 kau3 moa2 heng-cheng5). 嗚呼! Ai--chai3! Hak8 tu2-tu2 chian5, seng-khu i2-keng hoe3. Kun e5 si2 si7 Tai5-oan5 seng3-hoe7 e5 toa7 sng2-sit.
 KhoaN3 kun sui-jian5 hak8-bun7 tu2-chiah chiaN5 iau2-boe7 chhut-lai5 toa7 keng-eng5 ti7 sia7-hoe7; m7-ku2 kun e5 it-seng thang kong2 si7 tai7-piau2 hian7-tai7 Tai5-oan5 Chheng-lian5 e5 keng2-gu7. Si5-se3 e5 hoan2-tong7, houN3-hak8 bo5 ki-hoe7;u7 lang5 ui7-tioh8 hak8-chu e5 chou2-tong3, u7 lang5 ui7-tioh8 ke-teng5 sia7-hoe7 e5 m7 un2-chun2, ti3-kau3 poaN3-si3 kham2-kho2, khoaN3 hak8-bun7 chhin-chhiuN7 hai2-iuN5 bo5 chun5 thang koe3, chhin-chhiuN7 oah8-be2 pak8 ti7 si2-chhiu7; tui3 an2-ne khang-khang khng3 toa7 chi3-khi3 un2-bat8 ti7 san-lim5; che kiam2 m7-si7 hian7-tai7 Tai5-oan5 chheng-lian5 e5 keng2-gu7 mah? To7-siu kun e5 si2 si7 keng2-gu7 e5 hi-seng e5 chit8-e5. 嗚呼! eng7 kun e5 chai5 lai5 chhut-si3 ti7 50 ni5 i2-cheng5 e5 Tai5-oan5, bo5 hou7 goa7-kok bun5-beng5 e5 ap-pek, choan-sim ti7 si-bun5 han3-hak8, tek-khak si7 tah8 chheN e5 hun5 tit8-tit8 chiuN7. Eng7 kun e5 chai5 lai5 chhut-si3 ti7 50 ni5 i2-au7 e5 Tai5-oan5, hit-si5 pun2-to2 e5 kau3-iok8 kiam2-chhai2 khah chin2-heng, thak8 chheh e5 mng5 kiam2-chhai2 khah khui, thang sun7 chi3-khi3 sun7 ni5-hoe3 eng7 kang, kiam2-chhai2 bo5 koh-iuN7 lai7 chng3-a2 chhut phoe5-long5 goa7 e7 thang tek-chi3 ma7 ku2-kaN2. 嗚呼! kun chhoan3-chhoan3 chhut-si3 ti7 chit-tiap8 e5 Tai5-oan5, saN-tiN5 si3-tiN5 si5-chun7 koe3-choa khi3. Hong3-kiam tang-sai-iuN5 e5 hak8-bun7 na2 hoan5-chap8, ai3 gian2-kiu3 chio2 si5-chun7; khang-khang phau7 iu2-ui5 e5 chai5 khng3 oan2-tai7 e5 chi3, ut-chut koe3 chit8-si3-lang5. 嗚呼! goa2 chhim-chhim ui7-tioh8 kun e5 si2 sioh, soa3 ui7-tioh8 kun chi3-ai3 e5 peng5-iu2 Ng5 kun Hui7-ngou2, TiuN kun thiam-teng e5 si2 sioh, soa3 ui7-tioh8 hian7-tai7 Tai5-oan5 e5 chheng-lian5 lau5 chit8 phong2 tong5 cheng5 e5 bak8-sai2.
 Te7 chap8-peh se3-ki2 e5 tiong-iap8 Tek-kok u7 chit8 e5 chhut-mia5 e5 sian-seN mia5-kio3 Le5-sin3(Lessing) tu3 chhut-mia5 e5 si-jin5 Kou2-lai5-su-tek(Kleist) e5 toan7-ki3, tiong-kan u7 chit8 cham7 teh kong2, lang5 ti7 se3-kan u7 saN teng2-ho7: thau5 chit8 teng2-ho7 si7 thian-chu chin ho2, koh u7 chiau5-chng5 e5 ki-hoe7 thang poe5-iuN2 kau3 chiaN5-mih8, kau3-boe2 kian3-lip8 be7 hiu2-noa7 e5 kang-tiaN5 ti7 te7-bin7 chiuN7; chit ho7 lang5 han2-tit u7; Gi-seng3(Goethe)chiu7-si7 chit khoan2 e5 lang5. Te7-ji7 teng2-ho7 si7 sui-jian5 u7 chin ho2 e5 chai5, iau2-ku2 keng2-gu7 bo5 sun7-li7, sin-the2 m7 cho3 chu2, kau3 boe2 bo5 thang chhun-chhoa2 i e5 chai5-tiau7; put-ko3 sou2 boe7 bat kiaN5 e5 lou7 hou7 i tah8 koe3, khui chit8 tiau5-a2 lou7-hun5-a2; chit ho7 e5 lang5 khah che7 Nietzsche, a2-si7 Kleist si7 chhin-chhiuN7 chit khoan2. Te7-saN teng2-ho7 si7 sui-jian5 chai5-tiau7 khah peng5-siong5 iau2-ku2 u7 chin ho2 e5 keng2-gu7 thang pang-chan7 i tah8 thau5-cheng5 e5 lang5 e5 lou7 hou7 i khah toa7 tiau5; hian7-si5 e5 hak8-chia2 tu2-tu2 si7 an2-ne. Liau7 kun Sam-tiong7 e5 keng2-gu7 thang kong2 si7 siok8 ti7 teng2-bin7 sou2 kong2 e5 te7-ji7 teng2-ho7. Sim2-mih8 lang5 e7 phah bo5 ti7 chhau2-chhi3-a2 e5 tiong-kan khui lou7-hun5 e5 lang5 e5 kong-lo5? Toe3 au7-piah kiaN5 lou7 e5 lang5 bo5 hiah khoai3, cho3 thau5-cheng5 khui lou7 e5 koh-khah oh. Na7 chiong Tai5-oan5 hian7-si5 cheng-sin5-kai3 e5 hoan2-tong7 pi2-pheng7 chian3-cheng. Liau7 kun e5 si2 bo5 koh-iuN7, SoaN-tang Poan3-to2 chiuN7-liok8-au7 ui7-tioh8 khi3 tham3 khe-lau5, chit8-e5 siong7-teng2 peng tu2-tioh8 beng5-u7 chian3-si2. Sui-jian5 khui lou7 e5 lang5 si2, si7 beh bian2-le7 au7-sin e5 lang5; To7-siu kun e5 si2 e7 koh seN-chhut che7-che7 e5 To7-siu. Che si7 chho2 chit phiN bun5 e5 si5, siong-pi tiong seN-chhut chit8 chiong2 e5 ng3-bang7. To7-siu kun e5 si2 m7-si7 bo5 i3-su3. Goan7 ThiN-pe7 an-ui3 chiok-hok khi3 hou7 Liau7 kun Sam-tiong7 e5 hiaN-ti7 ke-koan3 kap chhin-chhek. 
 Teng2-bin7 sou2 ki3 Liau7 kun e5 li2-lek8 si7 chiau3 goa2 se3-han3 kap i cho3-hoe2 sou2 thiaN-kiN3 e5 lai5 sia2, kiam2-chhai2 u7 bo5 chiau5-pe7 e5 sou2-chai7, bang7 khoaN3 Po3 e5 liat8-ui7 khoan-iong5. 
